---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Der Town"
  description="Privacy policy for Der Town community platform. Learn how we protect your personal information and data when using our community events service."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 to-indigo-900 flex items-center justify-center py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-95 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-2xl w-full p-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Effective Date: May 7th, 2025</p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-800">This Privacy Policy describes how Der Town ("we", "our", or "us") collects and uses personal information submitted through this website.</p>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-6 text-gray-900">
        <li>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Information We Collect</h2>
          When you submit an event or announcement, we may collect:
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>Your name (if provided)</li>
            <li>Your email address (for follow-up, if provided)</li>
            <li>Event details (title, date, location, description)</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="block mt-2">This information is collected solely for the purpose of reviewing and posting community events.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          We use the submitted information to:
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 mt-2">
            <li>Publish events and announcements on our website</li>
            <li>Contact you for clarification, if necessary</li>
          </ul>
          <span class="block mt-2">We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Public Visibility</h2>
          Please be aware that event content you submit may be published and publicly accessible. While we do not post your email address or name unless explicitly requested, event details will be viewable by site visitors.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Data Storage</h2>
          Submissions may be stored securely in a database or email system for administrative purposes. We take reasonable measures to protect your information, but cannot guarantee absolute security.
        </li>
        <li>
          <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900 mb-1">Contact</h2>
          If you have questions or would like your information removed, contact us.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout> 